<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Order Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    /* General Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #444;
    }

    .container {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f9f9f9);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 750px;
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #1b998b;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .course-info {
      text-align: left;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .course-info h4 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #264653;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    table td {
      padding: 15px 10px;
      /* border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; */
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .first-td {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .table-row {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .second-td {
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }

    tr:hover {
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
    }

    .email-footer {
      /* background-color: #e0f7fa; */
      padding: 15px 0;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #004d40;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-footer a {
      color: #00796b;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .email-footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .cta-button {
      background-color: #1b998b;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background-color: #1a8f7f;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      table td {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        padding: 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="message-sm">
      <h1>Your CodeXBuddy01 E-learning Order is Confirmed!</h1>
      <p>We’re excited to help you start learning. Here are your order details:</p>
    </div>

    <div class="course-info">
      <h4>Order Summary:</h4>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>Order #: <strong><%= order._id %></strong></td>
          <td>Order Date: <strong><%= order.date %></strong></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table>
        <tr>
          <td class="first-td">Item</td>
          <td class="first-td">Qty</td>
          <td class="first-td">Cost</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td  class="second-td"><%= order.name %></td>
          <td  class="second-td">1</td>
          <td  class="second-td">₹<%= order.price %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #00000029;">
        <tr>
          <td style="text-align: left; padding-right: 10px;">Subtotal:</td>
          <td style="text-align: right;">₹<%= order.price %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="text-align: left; padding-right: 10px;">Total:</td>
          <td style="text-align: right;">₹<%= order.price %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <!-- Border after the last row -->
<hr style="border-top: 1px solid #00000029; margin: 20px 0;" />
    </div>

    <a href="https://codexbuddy01.in" class="cta-button" target="_blank">Visit our website</a>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:codexbuddy01@gmail.com">codexbuddy01@gmail.com</a></p>
      <p>&copy; 2024 CodeXBuddy01. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
